            </p>
          </feedback>
        </choice>

        <choice>
          <statement>
            <p>double</p>
          </statement>

          <feedback>
            <p>This method wants you to return a value that represents a day of the week. Does that need a decimal?</p>
          </feedback>
        </choice>

        <choice>
          <statement>
            <p>None, it's a constructor.</p>
          </statement>

